<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include("../partials/head", { title: "Home - Dance World" }) %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("../partials/header") %>

  <main>
    <h2>Welcome To My Dance World!</h2>
    <p>
        Dance is a form of creative expression through physical movement that includes rhythmic movements that accompany music. Historically, dance has been used in celebrations and religious observances. Dance has played an important role in human societies since ancient times and continues to evolve and develop today.
    </p>

    <% if (typeof danceButton !== "undefined") { %>
        <button id="danceButton" class="dance-btn" role="button">Start Dancing</button>
    <% } %>
  </main>

  <%- include("../partials/footer") %>

  <% if (typeof scripts !== "undefined") { %>
      <script src="/js/animation.js"></script>
  <% } %>
</body>
</html>
